Upon receiving the award at the PSL offices on Monday afternoon ever-hard working midfielder Manyama thanked his City teammates for helping to scoop the accolade.This season the 26-year-old has scored an impressive seven goals and helped steer his side to Nedbank Cup honours and to the top of the league standings. It s an honour and it has been a team effort to win this award Manyama said. I am taking this award for my teammates and everyone at Cape Town City from the staff to the technical team. Cape Town City s Eric Tinkler was named the best coach in the league for the month of December.SuperSport United coach Stuart Baxter won that prize for the months of October and November.- TMG Digital/TMG Sport